      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so u mentioned those three main groups, but how do they actually behave in day to day? like when u look at the different regions, is there a general pattern to how people act or how they view each other? i'm trying to get a sense of the cultural temperament in the north vs the south so we know what to expect from locals on the ground.",
